    What's new? Well now anyone who can walk and carry a weapon is here in the north. Some people keep hearing a voice that promises it'll grant you anything you wish.
    Anything. Can you imagine if someone says "I want the Zone to disappear"? No way! Warn other people to wish for something else. Spread the word! Or else we'll all be waking up in the middle of a field or a swamp. And worse, we'll all have to get jobs.


This city is full of brainwashed idiots, all drooling and slobbering at the mouth. And to think, a lot of them used to be the toughest of Stalkers. Scary stuff. Best be careful or else we'll end up like one of them.

Be careful of those stone-lickers. They're like cockroaches in these parts. They're absolutely everywhere.

Ever since I got past the Scorcher I've been wondering one thing. How the hell did that one Freedom squad manage to hold out here for a month? It's impossible. 

I heard about some members of Freedom who managed to survive in Pripyat for a whole month while cut off from the rest of the Zone. No idea how they did it. Maybe they just sat in an apartment with the lights off. 



